
# Grouper Project Layout

This file is intended to give you a brief overview of how the Grouper
directory tree is structured.

$Id: LAYOUT,v 1.15 2005-09-07 22:13:48 blair Exp $

---

## LICENSE

Grouper licensing information.

## README

Grouper README.

---

## build/

Destination for all compiled Java classes.

## build.xml

Ant build configuration file.

---

## conf/

Configuration directory.

### conf/ehcache.xml

Hibernate cache configuration file.

### conf/hibernate.properties

Hibernate configuration file.

### conf/Grouper.hbm.xml

Grouper's Hibernating mapping configuration file.

### conf/grouper.properties

Grouper configuration file.

### conf/log4j.properties

Logging configuration file.

### conf/sources.xml

Subject API resolver configuration file.

---

## contrib/

Contributed loaders, provisioners and other programs for use with
Grouper.  See _contrib/README_ for more information.

---

## dist/

### api/

Destination for javadoc-generated documentation.

### lib/

Destination for compiled .jar files.

### run/

HSQLDB data directory and log4j log directory.

---

## doc/

### API

API class and method summary.

### erd.jpg

Groups Registry ERD.

### GETTING_GROUPER

Information on obtaining Grouper via official releases, anonymous CVS
and periodic snapshots.

### grouper-impl-guide.html

Grouper implementation guide.

### javadoc/

Generated API javadoc.

### KNOWN_ISSUES

Known issues with the Grouper API and Groups Registry.

### LAYOUT

This file.

### NEWS

Release Notes.

### ROADMAP

Grouper development roadmap for future releases.

---

## java/

### lib/

Third-party jar files included with Grouper.  See _java/lib/README_ for
more details on the jar files included.

### src/

Grouper's Java source code.  

### tests/

Java source used for testing Grouper.

---

## sql/

### sql/generate-schema.sh

Generate SQL data files from the .m4 source files.

### sql/schema.m4

m4 source file used to generate database-specific schema files.

### sql/schema-hsqldb.sql

HSQLDB database schema specification.

### sql/schema-oracle.sql

Oracle database schema specification.

### sql/init.sql

Default Grouper schema.  Needed to use Grouper.

### sql/test-data.m4

m4 source file used to generate the test sql data.

### sql/test-data-hsqldb.sql

Test data needed for running the test harness with HSQLDB.

### sql/test-data-oracle.sql

Test data needed for running the test harness with Oracle.

